            <lg xml:id="TK82">
<l>viruntu puṟattatāt tāṉuṇṭal cāvā</l>
<l>marunteṉiṉum vēṇṭaṟpāṟ ṟaṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Eating by oneself with guests outside, though it be immortal</l>
<l>nectar, would not be desirable.</l>
